                                <div class="timeline-heading">
                                    <h4></h4>
                                    <h4 class="subheading">Sign in with Linkedin</h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="timeline-body">
                                    <p class="text-muted">Both Students and Sponsors can sign into our app with Linkedin. Once you sign in you will decide whether you are a student or a sponsor. If you are a student you will fill out a short survey about yourself. If you are a sponsor you can search for students who are not sponsored yet. Student can posts the needs that they have by showing proof of the need. </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="timeline-inverted">
                            <div class="timeline-image"><span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                                <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                                <i class="fa fa-search fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                                <!-- <img class="img-circle img-responsive" src="img/about/2.jpg" alt=""> -->
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-panel">
                                <div class="timeline-heading">
                                    <h4></h4>
                                    <h4 class="subheading">Searching for a Student</h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="timeline-body">
                                    <p class="text-muted">Once you find a student you would like to sponsor you can check out their profile and follow them. When you go to their profile and follow you can view their needs and offer challenges. Student can accept or deny a challenges and challenges are on a semester basis.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <div class="timeline-image">
                            <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                              <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                              <i class="fa fa-usd fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                              </span>
                               <!--  <img class="img-circle img-responsive" src="img/about/3.jpg" alt=""> -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-panel">
                                <div class="timeline-heading">
                                    <h4></h4>
                                    <h4 class="subheading">Sponsor</h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="timeline-body">
                                    <p class="text-muted">Once you have students that you want to sponsor you can decide to donate towards their goal for their need. Also there are four challenges: Increase GPA, Honors, Dean's List and Community Service. At the end of the semester the challenge is due and both students and sponsors have to confirm the completion.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
